node.text:
At this point, it’s not quite accurate to say there’s a crisis at the border. The situation is much worse than that. As a result of the policy changes enacted by Joe Biden, combined with an utter lack of planning or foresight about what those policies would produce, the border is now in chaos — and getting worse by the day.

Seems like everything Joe Biden touches turns to 💩

#usbp #borderpatrol #buildthewall #securetheborder #maga #makeamericagreatagain #bordercrisis #bidenbordercrisis #bidensucks #democratsdestroyamerica

node.text:
Several top officials from the ousted Western-backed government have gathered in the Panjshir Valley. They include Vice President Amrullah Saleh, who claims to be the caretaker leader after President Ashraf Ghani fled the country.

They have vowed to resist the Taliban and are calling for Western aid to help roll them back.

Most people don’t know that the VP of Afghanistan did not flee the country, but instead fled into the Panjshir Valley. 

“I watched this.  This man wants strength from the US.  Biden has shown the entire world he is WEAK.  My fears are we will have another 9/11 or worse. Biden lied saying the the Afghan soldiers gave up.  I am sick of Lyin Biden. When will people and those that are to represent us stand up, grow a set, and get down to business.  We have got to get OUR people out of Afghanistan and those that helped our troops. Joe Biden, Kamela Harris, Nancy Pelosi need to be removed from their respective offices and held for Treason.  Over 85 BILLION dollars of weapons were handed over to the enemy.  Not to mention the names of those who helped us. “

node.title: VP of Afghanistan wants strength from the U.S. but gets WEAKNESS

node.text:
This is truly a must-listen.

I’m crying right now listening to this phone call. It hit me like a freight train, I can feel her pain and anger all at the same time. 

20 yr old Rylee McCollum was one of the 13 Marines killed in the suicide bombing in Kabul.

His mom called into the Wilkow Majority Show on Sirius XM Channel 125. This is truly a must-listen.✅

Her representative @repboebert has reached out & is visiting her home. The White House has not.

node.text:
Afghan journalists were left severely battered and bruised after being beaten by the Taliban in Afghanistan for covering a women’s protest in Kabul.

Photographer Nematullah Naqdi and reporter Taqi Daryabi revealed their horrific injuries, including severe welts and bruising to their backs and legs. 

The pair say they were beaten with batons, electrical cables and whips after being detained for several hours by Taliban. 

“One of the Taliban put his foot on my head, crushed my face against the concrete. They kicked me in the head … I thought they were going to kill me,” Naqdi told Agence France-Presse.

These are the Taliban Joe Biden is now working with. 

Go figure!

node.text:
China weighing occupying U.S. Bagram Air Base in Afghanistan after "humiliating" U.S. withdrawal. 

In the wake of the United States' pullout from Afghanistan, China is looking to fill some of the real estate left behind in an attempt to strengthen ties with the Taliban and embarrass America. 

China is considering sending military personnel and economic development officials to Bagram Airfield, one of the most prominent and busiest American military bases in the world. 

Given their past experience, the Chinese must be eager to get their hands on whatever the U.S. has left at the base. 

US forces in Afghanistan abandoned the U.S. Bagram Military Base airport overnight in July - shutting off the lights and slipping away into the night without telling Afghan military commanders who were supposed to take it over. 

Joe Biden did this. He  ignored our military commanders, abandoned Americans in Afghanistan, created a foreign humanitarian crisis and handed over a U.S. Military Base leaving behind Billions of U.S. high tech military hardware. Only an idiot would do such a humiliating job and embarrass America.. 

But build back better 🤦🏻‍♂️

node.text:
“Did the US fund virus research in China?
“Yes, it did” ~ @bbcnews 

The U.S. did fund “gain of function” research in Wuhan.

Fauci lied.

Dr Fauci, as well as being an adviser to President Biden, is the director of the US National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases (NIAID), part of the US government's National Institutes of Health (NIH).”

“This body did give money to an organisation that collaborated with the Wuhan Institute of Virology.
That organisation - the US-based EcoHealth Alliance - was awarded a grant in 2014 to look into possible coronaviruses from bats.
EcoHealth received $3.7m from the NIH, $600,000 of which was given to the Wuhan Institute of Virology.
In 2019, its project was renewed for another five years, but then pulled by the Trump administration in April 2020 following the outbreak of the coronavirus pandemic.”

Seems like everything Joe Biden touches turns to 💩
